_sText:
This is my 2nd gungame map. I like to play on it and i hope you will like it too. 
The map is a marble-temple...marble floors, walls and columns. Pretty good for fast gungame rounds.  

The map contains 32 spawn points, so 16 terrorists and 16 counter-terrorists can play on it. 


Ask me if you want to edit and republish this map.
